  "text": "Total RNA was extracted from N. benthamiana leaves with Trizol reagent (Invitrogen) according to the manufacturer's instructions. Total RNA (10 mg) was separated on 1.2 % formaldehyde-agarose gels and transferred to Hybond-N+ membranes and UV cross-linked. Northern hybridization was performed as described previously [CITATION_1] , and signals were detected using a Typhoon 9200 imager (Amersham Pharmacia).",
